    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A–G. Edessa (E.) amaurata sp. n.: A–E, pygophore in dorsal, dorsolateral, ventral, posterior and posterolateral views, respectively; F, genital plates; G, metasternal process. vf 8—valvifer VIII; vf 9—valvifers IX; lat 8—laterotergite VIII; lat 9—laterotergite IX; X—tenth segment. Scale= 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

