    dc:description "FIGURE 44. A–G. Edessa (E.) simulata sp. n.: A–E, pygophore in dorsal, dorsolateral, ventral, posterior and posterolateral views, respectively; F, genital plates; G, metasternal process. Scale= 1 mm." ;
